    "long_instructions": "#Style Critique Conversation\r\n\r\n1. Upload the two website images from the Library.\r\n2. Chat with the AI about each site’s design and usability.\r\n   - Ask how readability, color contrast, consistency, and clarity affect the mood of each site.\r\n3. Discuss what works well and what could be improved.\r\n4. End your chat by summarizing your thoughts:\r\n   - One strength and one weakness for each website.\r\n   - One mood word that describes how each site feels (e.g., chaotic, calm, professional, playful).",
